<br>You: Yes

<br>Waitress: Hello sir. Welcome to our restaurant. Have you eaten here before?

<br>Customer: No. This is my first time here.

<br>Waitress: Oh. Well, would you like to hear about today’s specials?

<br>Customer: Sure, why not?

<br>Waitress: Ok. We have a 10 oz. stake with some mashed potatoes and a salad as your sides.

<br>Customer: Sounds good I would like some steak

<br>Waitress: Good choice. How would you like your steak?

<br>Customer: Medium rare.

<br>Waitress: Ok. What would you like to drink?

<br>Customer: Just some water please.

<br>Customer: No. I’m good. Thanks.

